---
title: Spiced Chicken Strips & Roast Veggie Couscous with Creamy Dill & Parsley Dressing
description: Colourful, nutritious and flavoursome - these are just a few of the ways we can describe this amazing veggie-loaded couscous. Topped with lightly spiced chicken and herbed yoghurt, your insides will love it just as much as your tastebuds do.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-strips-roast-veggie-couscous-c623684c.jpg
